# Example requests for ProductController

### Create a new product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sample Product",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "technicalDetailsJson": {
    "power": "100kW",
    "torque": "200Nm",
    "additionalProperties": {
      "weight": "1500kg",
      "dimensions": "4.5m x 1.8m x 1.5m"
    }
  },
  "descriptionJson": {
    "descriptions": {
      "en": "This is a sample product description in English",
      "de": "Dies ist eine Beispielproduktbeschreibung auf Deutsch"
    }
  }
}

### Update an existing product
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/2a1b7017-3fcc-4838-8931-70140647cc7c
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Product",
  "status": "INACTIVE",
  "technicalDetailsJson": {
    "power": "120kW",
    "torque": "250Nm",
    "additionalProperties": {
      "weight": "1600kg",
      "dimensions": "4.6m x 1.9m x 1.5m"
    }
  },
  "descriptionJson": {
    "descriptions": {
      "en": "This is an updated product description in English",
      "de": "Dies ist eine aktualisierte Produktbeschreibung auf Deutsch"
    }
  }
}

### Get product history
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/2a1b7017-3fcc-4838-8931-70140647cc7c/history
Accept: application/json

